snippet.title: OffRoad Legends - Launch Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
OffRoad Legends is available on  the Appstore & Android Market too: 
AppStore: http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/offroad-legends/id516875543
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dogbytegames.offroadlegendsfree
Site: http://www.dogbytegames.com/offroad_legends.html

Drive the most amazing offroad vehicles of all time in this extreme hill climbing madness!
Jump and fly above bottomless chasms with Monster Trucks, 4x4 off-roaders and
six wheeled Behemots!

Crash the Barriers!

Features:
- Four vehicle categories (Monsters, 4x4 off-roaders, Behemots, Fun cars)
- Three game modes
- Gorgeous graphics
- 56 challenging tracks
- Real time vehicle deformation
- Precise physics simulation
- Vehicle tuning
